title: Codex_Workbench
tags: examine codex hollow workbench
---
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
// The Codex — every examinable prop's tooltip.
// Author: Tobias Marrow (Worldbuilding & Lore Master)
// Spec:   Docs/Depth_Bible/Mission_1_2_Focus/03_SCENES_LANE_HOLLOW_GARDEN_COTTAGE.md
//         Docs/Depth_Bible/03_WORLDBUILDING_AND_LORE.md
// Guide:  Docs/GAMEPLAY_GUIDE_MISSION_1.md § 11, § 19
//         Docs/GAMEPLAY_GUIDE_MISSION_2.md § 13, § 25
//
// Discipline (Marrow Principle § 4):
//   • Every prop tooltip must do one of three things — tell the player
//     something about Marin (the predecessor), seed a long-arc story, or
//     warm the room. Never just describe geometry.
//   • One short paragraph per tooltip. Cozy register. No medical
//     vocabulary, no explicit grief, no fail states.
//   • The cozy player who examines all props in M1-2 receives the
//     hidden completion (Predecessor Trail Warmth +3 per prop).
// ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Codex: A worn workbench. Wood polished from a thousand hands before yours.
Codex: There is a circular indentation in the surface — orb-sized.

===

title: Codex_Kettle
tags: examine codex hollow kettle
---
Codex: A copper kettle, blackened at the bottom.
Codex: Marin's, by the dent.

===

title: Codex_Teapot
tags: examine codex hollow teapot
---
// Mission 1 Guide § 19.6 — "the village's small miracles."
Codex: This teapot has not been cold in twenty-two years.
Codex: The Keeper before you trained the wood stove to do that.
Codex: It is one of the village's small miracles.

===

title: Codex_HerbBasket
tags: examine codex hollow herbs
---
Codex: A small wicker basket.
Codex: There are leaves of lavender and a root of valerian inside.

===

title: Codex_Shelf_Empty
tags: examine codex hollow shelf
---
Codex: An empty shelf, dust-free. Waiting.

===

title: Codex_Shelf_WithDorisOrb
tags: examine codex hollow shelf doris
---
Codex: Doris's "First Loaves" rests on the shelf.
Codex: The amber glow is warm against your hand.

===

title: Codex_Apron
tags: examine codex hollow apron predecessor_seed
---
// Mission 1 Guide § 11.1 — predecessor seed #1.
Codex: A long brown apron. Pockets stuffed with old receipts.
Codex: The collar is frayed.
Codex: Whoever wore this stood at this bench every day for years.

<<adjust_predecessor_trail 3>>

===

title: Codex_Orb_Bee
tags: examine codex hollow welcome_orb bee
---
// Mission 1 Guide § 11.1, § 11.2 — welcome gift orb #1.
// Wedding Honey arc seed (Mission 3+).
Codex: A single bee suspended mid-flight inside a glass orb.
Codex: The bee is calm. It has been calm for at least three years.
Codex: The orb hums very faintly when you stand close to it.

<<adjust_predecessor_trail 3>>

===

title: Codex_Orb_Kettle
tags: examine codex hollow welcome_orb kettle_orb
---
// Mission 1 Guide § 11.2 — welcome gift orb #2.
// Marin's signature (Mission 4+).
Codex: An orb that contains the sound — only the sound — of a kettle just before it boils.
Codex: Holding the orb makes the room feel warmer by half a degree.

<<adjust_predecessor_trail 3>>

===

title: Codex_Orb_EmptyChair
tags: examine codex hollow welcome_orb empty_chair
---
// Mission 1 Guide § 11.2 — welcome gift orb #3.
// The predecessor's loss (Mission 6+).
Codex: An orb that appears, when you look at it closely, to contain a single wooden chair.
Codex: No one is in the chair. The chair is in late afternoon light.
Codex: You set it down quickly.

<<adjust_predecessor_trail 3>>

===

title: Codex_ReadingChairBook
tags: examine codex hollow book lampman
---
// Mission 1 Guide § 11.1, § 19.3 — the lampman folklore.
// The lampman will appear in Mission 7+ in a Memory Dream.
Codex: A book of regional folklore, open to the chapter on "the lampman."
Codex: The bookmark is a pressed yellow leaf.
Codex: The leaf is dry but the page is still slightly damp where a thumb rested.

<<adjust_predecessor_trail 3>>

===

title: Codex_Ledger_Closed
tags: examine codex hollow ledger
---
// Mission 1 Guide § 12.2.
Codex: A leather-bound book. The previous pages have been torn out.
Codex: The Keeper before you left you a clean book.

===

title: Codex_ToolRoll
tags: examine codex hollow tools
---
// Mission 1 Guide § 12.2 — Marin's polishing tools.
Codex: A leather roll of polishing tools.
Codex: They are clean. They have been used so many thousands of times
Codex: the wood is dark where Marin's thumb sat.

<<adjust_predecessor_trail 2>>

===

title: Codex_UpstairsBarrier
tags: examine codex hollow upstairs locked
---
