Codex: A wooden barrier marked "in repair."
Codex: The staircase behind it leads up.
Codex: You will need to wait.

===

title: Codex_GardenDoor_LockedM1
tags: examine codex hollow garden_door m1_locked
---
// Mission 1 — back door locked. Opens for Mission 2.
Codex: A small door. The garden is on the other side.
Codex: The hinge is stiff. It will open tomorrow morning.

===

